WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.628 --> 00:00:07.668
(Episode 20)

2
00:00:07.668 --> 00:00:09.037
- Hello. - Hello.

3
00:00:14.338 --> 00:00:16.107
Is Chef On's mother here today?

4
00:00:16.707 --> 00:00:19.207
I think she's at the terrace on the second floor.

5
00:00:24.317 --> 00:00:27.817
There seem to be less customers than usual today.

6
00:00:28.517 --> 00:00:30.657
Is it because of the allergy incident by any chance?

7
00:00:31.828 --> 00:00:32.987
How did you know?

8
00:00:35.057 --> 00:00:36.898
I found it out while researching data.

9
00:00:37.568 --> 00:00:39.797
You know, Good Soup is the background of my drama.

10
00:00:41.167 --> 00:00:44.708
Does this kind of incidents really affect your business?

11
00:00:45.038 --> 00:00:46.977
Rumors spread fast in this field.

12
00:00:47.438 --> 00:00:48.837
And fine dining restaurants like us...

13
00:00:48.837 --> 00:00:50.977
usually have fixed customers.

14
00:00:52.608 --> 00:00:55.877
When can we interview Min Ho, the youngest chef here?

15
00:00:58.447 --> 00:00:59.748
The work isn't tough.

16
00:01:03.458 --> 00:01:05.957
Or I tell myself it isn't hard.

17
00:01:06.358 --> 00:01:08.498
Are there any couples here?

18
00:01:08.858 --> 00:01:10.828
I'm fast to know in that kind of stuff.

19
00:01:12.028 --> 00:01:14.297
I think Soo Jung likes someone.

20
00:01:15.638 --> 00:01:16.668
And who is that?

21
00:01:22.338 --> 00:01:23.407
Here.

22
00:01:24.047 --> 00:01:25.377
Now, you ask me...

23
00:01:25.377 --> 00:01:27.677
to make cake for your interview?

24
00:01:27.677 --> 00:01:29.017
I need to win his favor.

25
00:01:29.278 --> 00:01:32.248
If he doesn't cooperate, I'll have a hard time writing my drama.

26
00:01:32.688 --> 00:01:34.618
I'll put your name on the list if it gets aired.

27
00:01:35.317 --> 00:01:37.888
"A cooking advisor, Choi Won Joon."

28
00:01:37.888 --> 00:01:38.927
Whatever.

29
00:01:39.157 --> 00:01:40.528
I just hope you become successful.

30
00:01:41.028 --> 00:01:42.998
You'll be at ease if you do well.

31
00:01:43.127 --> 00:01:46.097
Please go back to how you were in college.

32
00:01:46.868 --> 00:01:48.638
I won't go to you even if I change.

33
00:01:49.338 --> 00:01:50.537
I never told you to come to me.

34
00:01:51.468 --> 00:01:53.877
You think you have the lead in our relationship? You're wrong.

35
00:01:54.138 --> 00:01:56.237
It's going to be you who will feel bad if we don't date each other.

36
00:01:56.338 --> 00:01:58.507
Fix that short temper of yours.

37
00:02:00.478 --> 00:02:02.017
Look who's talking.

38
00:02:02.147 --> 00:02:03.847
Sometimes I laugh out of astonishment...

39
00:02:04.547 --> 00:02:06.017
whenever I talk with you.

40
00:02:06.017 --> 00:02:07.118
Laugh like that.

41
00:02:07.718 --> 00:02:10.428
Laugh no matter how much I throw a fit.

42
00:02:13.827 --> 00:02:14.928
I'll be going now.

43
00:02:17.627 --> 00:02:18.667
Excuse me.

44
00:02:18.968 --> 00:02:21.298
What do you do during your break time?

45
00:02:21.968 --> 00:02:25.007
We're free until we start preparing for dinnertime.

46
00:02:26.708 --> 00:02:27.838
What are you doing here?

47
00:02:28.338 --> 00:02:29.338
I'm covering this restaurant.

48
00:02:29.977 --> 00:02:31.947
- Is her story about cooking? - Yes.

49
00:02:31.947 --> 00:02:34.018
It might get filmed around next year since you're covering it now.

50
00:02:34.618 --> 00:02:37.648
Kyung, my drama is getting filmed this year.

51
00:02:37.648 --> 00:02:39.917
Her drama might as well get filmed.

52
00:02:39.917 --> 00:02:41.718
She has the synopsis and scripts for the first two episodes.

53
00:02:41.718 --> 00:02:42.988
When did she write all those?

54
00:02:42.988 --> 00:02:45.257
I heard she wrote it a few years ago.

55
00:02:46.757 --> 00:02:47.898
I should go.

56
00:02:48.827 --> 00:02:50.768
- Goodbye. - Bye.

57
00:02:52.067 --> 00:02:53.898
She's so diligent.

58
00:02:54.398 --> 00:02:56.268
No wonder why she's doing so well in her career.

59
00:02:57.067 --> 00:02:58.838
It's fine for her to be doing well,

60
00:02:59.407 --> 00:03:01.808
but I don't want her to be so rude to Chef Choi.

61
00:03:09.718 --> 00:03:10.887
Hello.

62
00:03:10.988 --> 00:03:13.118
- Hi. Have a seat. - Okay.

63
00:03:15.757 --> 00:03:18.088
- Did you see this? - No, I haven't.

64
00:03:19.327 --> 00:03:21.157
Gosh, he looks so handsome.

65
00:03:22.197 --> 00:03:23.227
Right?

66
00:03:24.398 --> 00:03:25.498
I gave birth to him.

67
00:03:26.268 --> 00:03:28.338
It's the best thing I've done in my entire life.

68
00:03:28.998 --> 00:03:30.768
The second best thing is getting divorced.

69
00:03:34.977 --> 00:03:36.708
I could finally live like a human after I got divorced.

70
00:03:37.447 --> 00:03:39.748
I don't know why I resisted so much not to divorce him then.

71
00:03:40.648 --> 00:03:42.447
Jung Sun suffered the most from it.

72
00:03:44.387 --> 00:03:46.447
I heard it was when he was 15.

73
00:03:46.847 --> 00:03:48.988
And he protected me at that age.

74
00:03:50.018 --> 00:03:52.287
I feel bad that he matured so early,

75
00:03:53.157 --> 00:03:54.257
but what can we do about it?

76
00:03:55.157 --> 00:03:57.868
Everyone is born with their own fate.

77
00:03:59.268 --> 00:04:00.798
He grew up so well.

78
00:04:01.097 --> 00:04:02.498
I have so many things to learn from him.

79
00:04:06.438 --> 00:04:07.907
I need to go shopping. You want to join me?

80
00:04:08.407 --> 00:04:11.308
Professor Min went for his special lecture, and Jung Sun has to work.

81
00:04:12.477 --> 00:04:14.317
Do you accompany with someone whenever you go shopping?

82
00:04:14.317 --> 00:04:15.548
Not always.

83
00:04:16.348 --> 00:04:18.817
You need to do something together to get closer with one another.

84
00:04:20.387 --> 00:04:23.158
Can I ask you something by the way?

85
00:04:24.158 --> 00:04:25.158
Sure. Ask away.

86
00:04:26.688 --> 00:04:28.598
Why do you want to get closer with me?

87
00:04:31.798 --> 00:04:34.238
You and I both date a younger man.

88
00:04:34.637 --> 00:04:36.337
You're dating my son too.

89
00:04:36.837 --> 00:04:38.507
It'd be great if we go on a double date.

90
00:04:38.967 --> 00:04:41.337
It might help my relationship with Professor Min.

91
00:04:43.238 --> 00:04:46.707
He makes me so happy.

92
00:04:47.717 --> 00:04:49.678
Jung Sun works every day,

93
00:04:50.447 --> 00:04:53.587
and I feel bad about it as his mom.

94
00:04:55.087 --> 00:04:58.928
I hope someone makes my son happy too.

95
00:04:59.387 --> 00:05:00.658
That's my wish.

96
00:05:02.957 --> 00:05:05.527
His face brightens whenever he talks about you.

97
00:05:06.127 --> 00:05:07.368
Really?

98
00:05:09.137 --> 00:05:11.408
You just made it so obvious that you're glad to hear that.

99
00:05:11.408 --> 00:05:12.438
I like it.

100
00:05:14.178 --> 00:05:16.108
I hate pretentious people.

101
00:05:16.877 --> 00:05:18.748
I can't go shopping with your because I have to work.

102
00:05:19.348 --> 00:05:20.748
I'm working on my drama at the moment.

103
00:05:21.147 --> 00:05:23.918
Now, you're being way too honest.

104
00:05:25.548 --> 00:05:28.788
I was a little intimidated by you when I first saw you.

105
00:05:29.517 --> 00:05:30.757
But now that I see you again,

106
00:05:31.827 --> 00:05:32.928
you're like a girl.

107
00:05:34.228 --> 00:05:35.327
I hear that often.

108
00:05:48.507 --> 00:05:50.038
- It's done. - Thank you.

109
00:05:50.038 --> 00:05:52.548
Please move to the chest X-ray room.

110
00:05:52.548 --> 00:05:53.647
- Okay. - Thank you.

111
00:05:54.678 --> 00:05:55.848
(Chest X-ray)

112
00:06:01.558 --> 00:06:03.658
Please move to the endoscopy room.

113
00:06:03.658 --> 00:06:04.688
- Okay. - Okay.

114
00:06:04.688 --> 00:06:05.728
We have an endoscopy next.

115
00:06:05.988 --> 00:06:07.998
- Lee Min Jae and Park Min Ah. - Here.

116
00:06:07.998 --> 00:06:09.257
Please wait here.

117
00:06:09.257 --> 00:06:10.267
- Okay. - Okay.

118
00:06:15.538 --> 00:06:17.368
You often have a headache these days.

119
00:06:17.668 --> 00:06:20.108
Should we have chosen to get a brain CT too?

120
00:06:20.507 --> 00:06:21.908
There's no need.

121
00:06:22.577 --> 00:06:24.548
Everyone has a slight headache in daily life.

122
00:06:24.978 --> 00:06:27.877
Still, it's good to get it checked while you're at it.

123
00:06:30.817 --> 00:06:33.288
All right, I'll listen to you.

124
00:06:34.217 --> 00:06:35.517
That makes me happy.

125
00:06:45.897 --> 00:06:47.637
What can I help you with, Mr. Park?

126
00:06:48.467 --> 00:06:51.067
I don't need anything fancy. Just show me bands.

127
00:07:17.728 --> 00:07:19.098
Are you developing a cake?

128
00:07:20.027 --> 00:07:21.767
It looks like a path in a forest.

129
00:07:22.298 --> 00:07:25.238
I'm sketching the cake Jung Woo will use for his proposal.

130
00:07:25.337 --> 00:07:26.567
Is Mr. Park getting married?

131
00:07:26.668 --> 00:07:29.577
Yes. I think there is someone he had on his mind for a while.

132
00:07:30.038 --> 00:07:31.348
It's a forest path concept.

133
00:07:31.348 --> 00:07:33.848
I want him and the woman he likes to walk on a flower path.

134
00:07:33.848 --> 00:07:35.048
I'm cheering for him.

135
00:07:35.577 --> 00:07:37.147
I'm so curious who it is.

136
00:07:37.587 --> 00:07:39.947
Don't worry, you'll see her on Saturday.

137
00:07:39.947 --> 00:07:41.158
It'll be here at Good Soup.

138
00:07:44.827 --> 00:07:46.587
- Hyun Soo. - Hello.

139
00:07:46.728 --> 00:07:49.498
- Are you here? - Yes. What are you doing?

140
00:07:49.627 --> 00:07:51.798
I'm sketching for a cake that will be used...

141
00:07:51.798 --> 00:07:52.897
for a proposal.

142
00:07:53.428 --> 00:07:55.397
Do you normally draw first before making it?

143
00:07:55.397 --> 00:07:57.608
Yes. The visuals are a part of the dish.

144
00:07:57.967 --> 00:07:59.007
What does it look like?

145
00:08:01.978 --> 00:08:03.178
It looks like a forest.

146
00:08:03.277 --> 00:08:04.308
I'll leave.

147
00:08:04.408 --> 00:08:06.108
- I'll go, Hyun Soo. - Okay.

148
00:08:06.178 --> 00:08:08.418
You should put in more flowers since it's a forest.

149
00:08:08.418 --> 00:08:09.918
I can make that happen.

150
00:08:14.188 --> 00:08:15.688
Can I try it too?

151
00:08:16.188 --> 00:08:17.228
Sure.

152
00:08:20.897 --> 00:08:21.928
Here?

153
00:08:26.798 --> 00:08:27.798
Again.

154
00:08:28.098 --> 00:08:29.168
(Son, kimchi, smell, Korean food)

155
00:08:29.168 --> 00:08:32.567
I made Kimchi soup at night by myself,

156
00:08:32.567 --> 00:08:35.138
and they somehow knew. They told me it smells.

157
00:08:35.138 --> 00:08:36.538
They knocked on my door...

158
00:08:39.107 --> 00:08:40.817
Are you serious?

159
00:08:41.048 --> 00:08:42.947
Why is he back?

160
00:08:49.418 --> 00:08:50.928
Gosh, I'm so tired.

161
00:08:50.928 --> 00:08:52.688
What is it again?

162
00:08:53.327 --> 00:08:55.258
I'll leave after napping for an hour.

163
00:08:55.258 --> 00:08:56.997
You can work continue doing your work.

164
00:08:57.097 --> 00:08:59.028
This isn't your home.

165
00:08:59.028 --> 00:09:00.898
Why do you always come here?

166
00:09:02.737 --> 00:09:05.367
Is Hyun Soo dating Chef On?

167
00:09:05.607 --> 00:09:08.138
Why do you care about someone else's personal life?

168
00:09:08.837 --> 00:09:11.447
Hyun Soo and I go way back.

169
00:09:12.607 --> 00:09:14.278
What will happen to Jung Woo, then?

170
00:09:16.778 --> 00:09:18.388
(Listen to the recording.)

171
00:09:20.317 --> 00:09:23.827
Does Mr. Park like Hyun Soo?

172
00:09:24.658 --> 00:09:26.128
It's been a long time.

173
00:09:28.398 --> 00:09:29.528
You woke me up.

174
00:09:30.768 --> 00:09:32.597
Can you make me ramyeon?

175
00:09:33.938 --> 00:09:35.538
Make it yourself.

176
00:09:36.398 --> 00:09:37.467
All right.

177
00:09:47.518 --> 00:09:49.778
Are you kidding me?

178
00:09:50.018 --> 00:09:51.648
Are you a child?

179
00:09:52.148 --> 00:09:53.418
Go away!

180
00:09:53.717 --> 00:09:55.357
My hands slipped.

181
00:09:55.357 --> 00:09:58.327
Go over there. Just sit down. I'll make it for you.

182
00:10:01.827 --> 00:10:04.168
Writer Kyung Ah, you're so kind.

183
00:10:06.898 --> 00:10:09.438
It's Kyung, not Kyung Ah.

184
00:10:09.538 --> 00:10:11.837
I hate it when people call me a writer.

185
00:10:11.837 --> 00:10:14.577
I also hate people that always say the things I hate.

186
00:10:15.378 --> 00:10:18.347
You're so mean. You're cruel.

187
00:10:20.107 --> 00:10:21.247
Do you like me now?

188
00:10:21.918 --> 00:10:23.648
Just don't talk to me.

189
00:10:24.648 --> 00:10:27.518
Don't I have pretty eyes?

190
00:10:29.058 --> 00:10:31.158
I'll tell you who has pretty eyes.

191
00:10:31.428 --> 00:10:33.628
If you go to Good Soup,

192
00:10:33.628 --> 00:10:36.058
there is a chef named On Jung Sun.

193
00:10:36.697 --> 00:10:38.268
I don't like him.

194
00:10:38.628 --> 00:10:40.737
He's my enemy as well as Jung Woo's.

195
00:10:41.237 --> 00:10:43.867
Gosh. What an embarrassment.

196
00:10:43.867 --> 00:10:45.638
You're embarrassing.

197
00:10:47.908 --> 00:10:49.477
You're friends with Ji Hong Ah, right?

198
00:10:49.607 --> 00:10:51.077
She's going to debut.

199
00:10:52.048 --> 00:10:53.717
Don't compare me to her!

200
00:10:53.918 --> 00:10:55.878
She stole my pride.

201
00:11:16.067 --> 00:11:18.408
Hello. It's been a while.

202
00:11:18.508 --> 00:11:19.967
I went on a business trip.

203
00:11:20.308 --> 00:11:21.737
Do you plan on going on TV again?

204
00:11:22.077 --> 00:11:23.138
No, I don't.

205
00:11:24.008 --> 00:11:25.008
How is it?

206
00:11:25.247 --> 00:11:26.447
It's delicious.

207
00:11:26.918 --> 00:11:28.847
It's a little different from when I had...

208
00:11:28.847 --> 00:11:30.987
oysters and champagne separately in the Mediterranean.

209
00:11:32.548 --> 00:11:33.888
It tastes completely different.

210
00:11:35.058 --> 00:11:36.117
Enjoy.

211
00:11:37.357 --> 00:11:38.428
Enjoy.

212
00:11:42.997 --> 00:11:44.067
You came alone?

213
00:11:44.428 --> 00:11:46.327
It's rare for you to not have a meeting.

214
00:11:47.067 --> 00:11:48.898
I'm trying not to take meetings.

215
00:11:49.367 --> 00:11:50.737
You fixed it.

216
00:11:51.107 --> 00:11:53.067
It tastes so much better than the first time.

217
00:11:54.038 --> 00:11:55.808
It's all thanks to a good taster.

218
00:11:57.648 --> 00:11:58.908
Let's have tea when you're done.

219
00:12:03.178 --> 00:12:04.487
Your restaurant is getting empty.

220
00:12:05.817 --> 00:12:08.617
I think I'll try changing the main dish next month.

221
00:12:08.857 --> 00:12:10.758
I don't think it's because of your cooking.

222
00:12:11.487 --> 00:12:12.888
Are you turning a blind eye to reality?

223
00:12:13.258 --> 00:12:17.528
I'm skeptical about solving problems in a realistic way.

224
00:12:17.867 --> 00:12:20.097
I have a feeling that's not where the essence is.

225
00:12:21.298 --> 00:12:24.168
Even after all that, I feel like I'm back where I began.

226
00:12:28.178 --> 00:12:29.508
About the restaurant...

227
00:12:30.138 --> 00:12:31.148
Yes?

228
00:12:31.908 --> 00:12:33.378
Why did you call it Good Soup?

229
00:12:33.878 --> 00:12:35.217
There's On Jung Sun.

230
00:12:35.477 --> 00:12:37.617
Sincerity and Love Line.

231
00:12:38.018 --> 00:12:39.288
You have so many options.

232
00:12:39.487 --> 00:12:41.617
My online nickname is Kind Soup.

233
00:12:41.617 --> 00:12:42.817
I got it from that.

234
00:12:43.058 --> 00:12:44.388
How can a soup be kind?

235
00:12:45.028 --> 00:12:47.258
There's soup...

236
00:12:47.258 --> 00:12:48.658
in Korean food too.

237
00:12:49.097 --> 00:12:50.567
You can have a meal with just a soup.

238
00:12:51.268 --> 00:12:52.467
I like being kind.

239
00:12:53.898 --> 00:12:55.398
I wanted to cook.

240
00:12:55.867 --> 00:12:58.438
"Good" to mean kind, and "soup" is from abroad.

241
00:12:58.438 --> 00:13:00.067
It's a meeting between the east and the west.

242
00:13:00.707 --> 00:13:03.477
You went through such a complicated process for the name.

243
00:13:03.477 --> 00:13:05.408
I didn't come up with it easily.

244
00:13:15.432 --> 00:13:18.664
