249
00:13:45.518 --> 00:13:46.717
I guess you beat me to it.

250
00:13:48.087 --> 00:13:49.918
- Jung Sun. - Yes?

251
00:13:52.457 --> 00:13:53.857
Do you know that I like you?

252
00:13:53.857 --> 00:13:55.658
Do you know that I like you?

253
00:13:56.097 --> 00:13:57.128
I do.

254
00:13:57.398 --> 00:13:58.467
Me too.

255
00:14:00.197 --> 00:14:01.298
However,

256
00:14:02.768 --> 00:14:05.367
we all have different priorities in our lives.

257
00:14:06.768 --> 00:14:09.438
I've seen many relationships break...

258
00:14:09.737 --> 00:14:10.747
in my time.

259
00:14:12.408 --> 00:14:13.778
Same with me.

260
00:14:14.648 --> 00:14:15.918
How will it be for us?

261
00:14:18.788 --> 00:14:20.518
If things break between us...

262
00:14:20.518 --> 00:14:22.717
Why would you think about that? It's good right now.

263
00:14:23.158 --> 00:14:24.827
We can worry about that if the time comes.

264
00:14:28.058 --> 00:14:31.528
Jung Woo. I don't think it'll ever change between us.

265
00:14:33.097 --> 00:14:34.097
Why not?

266
00:14:35.337 --> 00:14:36.467
Because you're you.

267
00:14:41.008 --> 00:14:42.237
Did I just move you?

268
00:14:45.648 --> 00:14:47.477
I still can't stop myself.

269
00:14:48.977 --> 00:14:50.817
I must go until the end and find out.

270
00:14:52.148 --> 00:14:53.317
What do you mean?

271
00:15:21.018 --> 00:15:22.247
Hello, Honey.

272
00:15:23.018 --> 00:15:24.918
I woke up early to work.

273
00:15:27.158 --> 00:15:28.357
Good luck!

274
00:15:36.327 --> 00:15:38.997
(Please close the door.)

275
00:15:39.798 --> 00:15:41.268
We still have a lot of puree left, right?

276
00:15:41.268 --> 00:15:43.097
- Yes, Chef. - Keep checking on it.

277
00:15:43.367 --> 00:15:45.237
Ha Sung, check on the seafood.

278
00:15:45.337 --> 00:15:46.607
Throw them out if you think they're not fresh.

279
00:15:46.607 --> 00:15:47.638
Okay.

280
00:15:53.617 --> 00:15:55.018
I'm here, Mr. Park.

281
00:15:58.117 --> 00:15:59.418
You look well.

282
00:15:59.617 --> 00:16:01.258
It's because I'm doing what I love.

283
00:16:01.717 --> 00:16:03.018
I went did some research yesterday.

284
00:16:03.217 --> 00:16:05.258
I plan on writing all day today.

285
00:16:05.658 --> 00:16:06.928
Why did you want to see me?

286
00:16:07.628 --> 00:16:08.928
I read your script.

287
00:16:11.067 --> 00:16:12.097
It was good.

288
00:16:13.697 --> 00:16:15.097
I told you.

289
00:16:15.337 --> 00:16:16.597
I'll contact the actors.

290
00:16:17.008 --> 00:16:20.237
I know you need stars as it's your debut drama.

291
00:16:20.438 --> 00:16:21.707
I'll make sure of it.

292
00:16:21.707 --> 00:16:22.808
Thank you.

293
00:16:24.308 --> 00:16:25.477
What about the director?

294
00:16:26.878 --> 00:16:28.947
The director?

295
00:16:29.778 --> 00:16:31.217
Direction is very important.

296
00:16:31.747 --> 00:16:34.487
The actors won't choose to sign just from looking at the writer.

297
00:16:35.087 --> 00:16:36.518
Not unless you're famous.

298
00:16:36.928 --> 00:16:38.327
So who will it be?

299
00:16:38.327 --> 00:16:39.827
I found someone fitting for you.

300
00:16:40.327 --> 00:16:42.827
I can't tell you right now. I'll tell you later.

301
00:16:44.168 --> 00:16:46.367
Is Hyun Soo's drama starting soon?

302
00:16:46.938 --> 00:16:49.638
She's editing right now. We'll have to talk after that.

303
00:16:50.168 --> 00:16:51.908
I trust you.

304
00:16:52.938 --> 00:16:54.408
Don't break the rules.

305
00:16:54.607 --> 00:16:57.207
If you neglect my drama because of Hyun Soo's,

306
00:16:57.207 --> 00:16:58.447
I won't sit still.

307
00:16:58.548 --> 00:16:59.908
You don't have to tell me.

308
00:17:03.018 --> 00:17:04.547
Hyun Soo and Jung Sun...

309
00:17:05.447 --> 00:17:06.648
are in love.

310
00:17:07.787 --> 00:17:11.527
There won't be any room for you in between them.

311
00:17:13.128 --> 00:17:14.257
Why are you telling me that?

312
00:17:15.957 --> 00:17:17.428
Because I like you.

313
00:17:19.197 --> 00:17:20.568
Even if you get hurt,

314
00:17:21.467 --> 00:17:22.967
it'd be good to know in advance.

315
00:17:39.088 --> 00:17:40.388
What are you doing here?

316
00:17:40.888 --> 00:17:42.487
Aren't you almost finished with shooting?

317
00:17:42.487 --> 00:17:44.727
Yes. See you.

318
00:17:56.767 --> 00:17:57.838
It must be tough.

319
00:17:58.338 --> 00:17:59.368
Sure, I guess.

320
00:17:59.737 --> 00:18:01.207
What would you like to drink?

321
00:18:02.408 --> 00:18:05.507
I don't need anything. Let's hear why you wanted to see me.

322
00:18:10.217 --> 00:18:12.918
I heard you're leaving the company.

323
00:18:13.487 --> 00:18:15.118
You're in talks with a couple of people.

324
00:18:15.118 --> 00:18:16.158
And?

325
00:18:16.487 --> 00:18:17.987
I want to scout you.

326
00:18:19.388 --> 00:18:20.797
I thought you didn't like me.

327
00:18:21.328 --> 00:18:24.098
That's separate. I admit that you're talented.

328
00:18:24.868 --> 00:18:27.967
I think we could be good partners if we can agree.

329
00:18:31.737 --> 00:18:32.737
I'd like some tea.

330
00:18:33.707 --> 00:18:34.737
Sure.

331
00:18:40.178 --> 00:18:42.047
Do you work on a Saturday?

332
00:18:43.477 --> 00:18:44.547
Yes.

333
00:18:45.017 --> 00:18:48.918
I have to do something very important today.

334
00:19:21.257 --> 00:19:22.287
It's so pretty.

335
00:19:22.717 --> 00:19:25.388
Mr. Park's proposal will succeed thanks to this cake.

336
00:19:27.257 --> 00:19:28.297
Right.

337
00:19:31.797 --> 00:19:34.098
(Lee Hyun Soo)

338
00:19:37.408 --> 00:19:38.467
Hello?

339
00:19:39.507 --> 00:19:40.578
What are you doing?

340
00:19:41.277 --> 00:19:42.338
I'm in a meeting.

341
00:19:42.537 --> 00:19:46.108
The synopsis is finished, so I was talking to Joon Ha and Kyung.

342
00:19:46.918 --> 00:19:47.977
Are you busy tonight?

343
00:19:48.747 --> 00:19:50.217
No, I'll be home all day.

344
00:19:51.088 --> 00:19:52.947
Then do you want to have dinner tonight?

345
00:19:53.247 --> 00:19:54.318
Are you free?

346
00:19:54.858 --> 00:19:57.727
I'll make myself free if it's you asking me.

347
00:19:58.388 --> 00:19:59.388
See you later.

348
00:20:01.557 --> 00:20:02.828
Are you asking Hyun Soo to come too?

349
00:20:03.358 --> 00:20:05.128
I'll introduce her officially to him.

350
00:20:05.428 --> 00:20:06.967
He'll be so surprised.

351
00:20:20.878 --> 00:20:21.977
(Lee Hyun Soo)

352
00:20:29.787 --> 00:20:30.787
Yes, Mr. Park.

353
00:20:31.957 --> 00:20:33.027
Come out right now.

354
00:20:33.828 --> 00:20:35.828
Pardon? Right now?

355
00:20:36.398 --> 00:20:38.697
Come out. Let's have dinner.

356
00:20:39.967 --> 00:20:43.608
Does it have to be tonight?

357
00:20:44.068 --> 00:20:45.307
I have plans.

358
00:20:46.007 --> 00:20:47.237
It has to be tonight.

359
00:20:48.037 --> 00:20:49.307
Let me add on that.

360
00:20:50.277 --> 00:20:51.777
You don't have a choice.

361
00:20:52.777 --> 00:20:53.818
I know.

362
00:20:55.477 --> 00:20:56.517
All right.

363
00:20:57.118 --> 00:20:59.088
Do whatever you want...

364
00:20:59.388 --> 00:21:01.057
until "Unruly Detectives" is finished.

365
00:21:16.068 --> 00:21:17.237
(Lee Hyun Soo)

366
00:21:19.838 --> 00:21:21.037
Why are you calling me?

367
00:21:21.408 --> 00:21:23.108
I don't think I can go tonight.

368
00:21:23.108 --> 00:21:24.878
Something came up. I'm sorry.

369
00:21:25.977 --> 00:21:27.217
It's okay.

370
00:21:27.648 --> 00:21:29.378
You and I can see each other any day.

371
00:21:29.848 --> 00:21:30.848
Thank you.

372
00:21:31.588 --> 00:21:34.017
Jung Sun, you're so warm like the sun.

373
00:21:35.358 --> 00:21:38.257
Don't make fun of me because you're sorry.

374
00:22:38.348 --> 00:22:41.318
You wanted to go to Good Soup?

375
00:22:42.457 --> 00:22:43.517
Yes.

376
00:22:44.688 --> 00:22:45.688
Are you happy?

377
00:22:46.727 --> 00:22:47.727
Yes.

378
00:22:52.628 --> 00:22:56.168
I told you I have something to tell you, right?

379
00:22:57.138 --> 00:22:58.338
Something personal...

380
00:22:59.908 --> 00:23:01.037
Let's talk inside.

381
00:23:21.457 --> 00:23:23.428
Hello, Mr. Park. Ms. Lee.

382
00:23:24.928 --> 00:23:27.398
Chef On was waiting. I'll lead you in.

383
00:23:41.717 --> 00:23:43.947
We'll seat ourselves. You can go.

384
00:23:44.017 --> 00:23:45.588
- We're not real customers anyway. - Okay.

385
00:23:51.557 --> 00:23:52.858
Why is it so pretty?

386
00:23:55.227 --> 00:23:56.557
Is it a special day?

387
00:24:06.737 --> 00:24:08.408
- Min Ho, bring that over. - Okay.

388
00:24:08.408 --> 00:24:10.507
- Ha Sung, taste the puree. - Yes, Chef.

389
00:24:10.507 --> 00:24:11.578
(Steak)

390
00:24:13.108 --> 00:24:14.848
There are 2 dinner courses for table 3.

391
00:24:14.848 --> 00:24:16.348
Medium rare for the steaks.

392
00:24:16.348 --> 00:24:17.418
- Yes, Chef. - Yes, Chef.

393
00:24:20.318 --> 00:24:22.318
Chef, Mr. Park is here.

394
00:24:22.618 --> 00:24:23.658
Okay.

395
00:25:05.928 --> 00:25:06.997
Jung Sun.

396
00:25:13.838 --> 00:25:17.547
If the woman you like likes another man,

397
00:25:18.247 --> 00:25:19.277
will you give up?

398
00:25:20.517 --> 00:25:22.818
I might give up, but not before I give it my all.

399
00:25:24.547 --> 00:25:26.447
Then what if that man was me?

400
00:25:27.918 --> 00:25:28.918
Would you still go all the way?

401
00:25:30.688 --> 00:25:31.928
Of course.

402
00:25:32.358 --> 00:25:33.428
Wouldn't you do the same?

403
00:25:36.497 --> 00:25:38.027
Let me introduce you two properly.

404
00:25:41.598 --> 00:25:43.138
He's the man I like the most.

405
00:25:53.747 --> 00:25:55.447
This is the woman I like the most.

406
00:26:18.237 --> 00:26:20.608
(Temperature of Love)

407
00:26:21.477 --> 00:26:22.608
Did you see Mr. Park's girlfriend?

408
00:26:22.608 --> 00:26:24.707
Did you know that I was dating Hyun Soo?

409
00:26:24.707 --> 00:26:26.608
- I did. - You knew,

410
00:26:26.648 --> 00:26:28.418
yet you asked me to help you with your proposal?

411
00:26:28.418 --> 00:26:30.717
I know it won't change anything no matter who gets involved.

412
00:26:30.717 --> 00:26:32.547
Hello, I'm Yoo Hye Jung.

413
00:26:32.547 --> 00:26:33.957
Let's have dinner since we're out.

414
00:26:33.957 --> 00:26:36.017
Did Mr. Park and Hyun Soo come together?

415
00:26:36.017 --> 00:26:38.358
I didn't do anything wrong, but I feel guilty.

416
00:26:38.358 --> 00:26:40.128
Let me have him.

417
00:26:40.128 --> 00:26:41.457
You won't keep him anyway.

418
00:26:41.457 --> 00:26:42.928
Hyun Soo and I are in love.

419
00:26:42.928 --> 00:26:45.628
I already know. Are you telling me because you're insecure?

420
00:26:45.727 --> 00:26:48.368
Isn't it childish? This is how it's like to fight for blind love.

421
00:26:48.697 --> 00:26:49.967
Can you handle it?

